title: Tech set for 94th Clyde Littlefield Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech set for 94th Clyde Littlefield Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The Texas track and field team will partake in the in the 94th Clyde Littlefield Texas Relays presented by Truist at Mike A. Myers Stadium. Tech will start competing Thursday and into Saturday.
